snippet.title: D.R.O.N.E. Announcement Trailer [HD - 1440p]
snippet.description:
D.R.O.N.E. is a sci-fi multiplayer arena shooter with an unprecedented amount of creative freedom. Be part of our community and help us in our preparation for crowdfunding. Make sure to like, subscribe and share! 

For more info, screenshots and videos visit our site: http://dronethegame.com

Join our social media:
http://facebook.com/dronethegame
http://twitter.com/drone_the_game
